.\" Man page for claude-dotfiles update.sh
.\" To view: man ./man/man1/claude-dotfiles-update.1
.TH CLAUDE\-DOTFILES\-UPDATE 1 "May 2026" "claude-dotfiles 1.5.0" "Claude Code Tools"
.SH NAME
claude\-dotfiles\-update \- pull the latest claude-dotfiles and redeploy symlinks
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B bash
.I <dotfiles\-dir>/scripts/update.sh
.RI [ OPTIONS ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Pulls the latest changes from the remote claude-dotfiles repository and
re-runs \fBsetup.sh\fR to ensure all symlinks and config files are current.
Safe to re-run at any time.
.PP
The update does \fInot\fR update your personal config repo. Manage that repo
separately with \fBgit pull\fR.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-h ", " \-\-help
Show usage summary and exit.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Update completed successfully.
.TP
.B 1
git pull or setup failed.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
Update claude-dotfiles:
.B bash ~/.local/share/claude-dotfiles/scripts/update.sh
.TP
Using the alias added by install.sh:
.B claude-update
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR claude-dotfiles (1),
.BR claude-dotfiles-setup (1),
.BR claude-dotfiles-status (1)
.SH AUTHOR
Spyced Concepts Ltd. <https://spycedconcepts.co.uk>
